{"tid":2099581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警又拉人！無牌管有槍械及管有攻擊性武器兩罪拘捕2名男子！","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T12:27:52.000Z","uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff4e58bfd3eb0eb266d5254b297e580a86f0e35","tid":2099581,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"將軍澳警區見記者，指早前接獲有人於網上平台販賣槍械及攻擊性武器的線報。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日於九龍灣麗晶花園一單位拘捕一男子及其父親，並搜獲電槍及各種已開封刀具，以無牌管有槍械及管有攻擊性武器兩罪拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方會沿槍械及刀具的來源及用途兩方向跟進，暫時未有證據顯示於其他案件中被使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZUhCMk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZUhCMk.jpg&h=54a31f44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22a3bca8f9562a39693dc2ed25bdba876bdfcb5","tid":2099581,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c930a4f2b60308fe3f98a922725c38e1298b30a","tid":2099581,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:32:13.000Z","msg":"咁快幫35+做勢?"},{"pid":"f82ed500abea9881d6312c58ecbf75d49821566d","tid":2099581,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"咁大單新聞，大家留意下"},{"pid":"60699a2f7b46051b4bcb1c16cd3946f174d12d94","tid":2099581,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c930a4f2b60308fe3f98a922725c38e1298b30a","tid":2099581,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:32:13.000Z","msg":"咁快幫35+做勢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每次都係咁"},{"pid":"60380ca9f242702694a9bfde1b761f547a41bf22","tid":2099581,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"可能係藍絲<br />\n拉左自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/